{{!--
  Internal Case Template
  Task: 2.4
  Purpose: Generate internal business case for deal review with economics, context, risks
--}}
You are a deal team lead preparing an internal business case for leadership review and go/no-go decision.

## Deal Context
Organization: {{organization.name}}
Industry: {{organization.industry}}
Company Size: {{organization.size}}
Deal Stage: {{deal.stage}}
Expected Close Date: {{deal.expectedCloseDate}}
Value Case: {{valueCase.title}}
Case ID: {{valueCase.id}}

## Deal Economics
{{#if deal.economics}}
- Annual Contract Value: {{deal.economics.acv}}
- Total Contract Value: {{deal.economics.tcv}}
- Contract Term: {{deal.economics.term}} years
- Expansion Potential: {{deal.economics.expansionPotential}}
- Services Component: {{deal.economics.servicesValue}}
{{/if}}

## Value Analysis Summary
{{#if valueModel}}
Total Quantified Value: {{valueModel.totalValue.low}} to {{valueModel.totalValue.high}} {{valueModel.totalValue.unit}}
Value-to-Price Ratio: {{valueModel.vpRatio}}
{{/if}}

{{#each valueModel.drivers}}
- {{name}}: {{impactRange.low}} to {{impactRange.high}} {{unit}} ({{confidence}} confidence)
{{/each}}

## Competitive Context
{{#if competitors}}
Primary Competitors:
{{#each competitors}}
- {{name}}: {{positioning}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

{{#if competitiveAdvantages}}
Our Advantages:
{{#each competitiveAdvantages}}
- {{advantage}}: {{supportingEvidence}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

{{#if competitiveRisks}}
Competitive Risks:
{{#each competitiveRisks}}
- {{risk}}: {{mitigationStrategy}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

## Risk Assessment
{{#each risks}}
- {{category}}: {{description}}
  Likelihood: {{likelihood}} | Impact: {{impact}} | Mitigation: {{mitigation}}
{{/each}}

## Assumption Quality Summary
{{#each assumptions}}
- {{description}}: Quality {{quality}} (validated: {{#if validated}}yes{{else}}partial/no{{/if}})
{{/each}}

## Integrity Check Results
Overall Score: {{integrity.score}}
Veto Decision: {{#if integrity.veto}}VETOED{{else}}PASSED{{/if}}
{{#if integrity.criticalIssues}}
Critical Issues:
{{#each integrity.criticalIssues}}
- {{this}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

## Task
Compose an internal business case for deal review (500-700 words) that:
1. Summarizes deal economics and strategic value
2. Presents the competitive landscape and our positioning
3. Lists all risk factors with likelihood, impact, and mitigation strategies
4. Provides an honest assessment of assumption quality
5. Notes any integrity issues that could derail the deal
6. Recommends clear next steps with owners and timeframes

The tone should be internal-ready: thorough, candid, and decision-oriented.

Return valid JSON matching this schema:
{
  "title": "Internal Business Case: {{valueCase.title}}",
  "deal_summary": {
    "acv": "string",
    "tcv": "string",
    "term_years": "number",
    "quantified_value_range": "string",
    "vp_ratio": "string",
    "strategic_importance": "string (high/medium/low with rationale)"
  },
  "value_analysis": {
    "total_quantified_value": {
      "low": "string",
      "high": "string",
      "unit": "string"
    },
    "key_drivers": [
      {
        "name": "string",
        "impact": "string",
        "confidence": "number",
        "claim_id": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "competitive_context": {
    "primary_competitors": [
      {
        "name": "string",
        "positioning": "string",
        "threat_level": "string (high/medium/low)"
      }
    ],
    "our_advantages": ["string"],
    "competitive_risks": [
      {
        "risk": "string",
        "mitigation": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "risk_assessment": [
    {
      "category": "string",
      "description": "string",
      "likelihood": "string (high/medium/low)",
      "financial_impact": "string",
      "mitigation": "string",
      "owner": "string"
    }
  ],
  "assumption_quality": {
    "overall_rating": "string (high/medium/low)",
    "critical_assumptions": [
      {
        "assumption": "string",
        "quality": "string",
        "validated": "boolean",
        "evidence_strength": "string"
      }
    ],
    "gaps": ["string (unvalidated assumptions that need work)"]
  },
  "integrity_status": {
    "score": "number",
    "vetoed": "boolean",
    "critical_issues": ["string"],
    "recommended_actions": ["string"]
  },
  "recommendation": {
    "decision": "string (proceed/conditional/defer/pass)",
    "conditions": ["string (if conditional)"],
    "rationale": "string"
  },
  "next_steps": [
    {
      "action": "string",
      "owner": "string",
      "deadline": "string",
      "priority": "string (high/medium/low)"
    }
  ],
  "provenance_refs": ["array of claim IDs used"]
}

Every value claim must include its provenance reference in claim_id fields.
